{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":690,"text":"So, imagine that you take\na 19-hour, very long drive"},{"time":8022,"text":"to Disney World,"},{"time":9366,"text":"with two kids in the back seat."},{"time":12256,"text":"And 15 minutes into this 19-hour trip,"},{"time":18531,"text":"the immutable laws of nature dictate"},{"time":21269,"text":"that you get the question:"},{"time":23349,"text":"\"Are we there yet?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":24737,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":26549,"text":"So you answer this question\na hundred more times, easily,"},{"time":30030,"text":"in the negative,"},{"time":31213,"text":"but you finally arrive."},{"time":32637,"text":"You have a wonderful,\nwonderful, wonderful trip."},{"time":35434,"text":"You drive 19 long hours back home."},{"time":41538,"text":"And when you get there,"},{"time":43099,"text":"the police are waiting on you."},{"time":45221,"text":"They accuse you of committing a crime"},{"time":47633,"text":"that occurred while you\nwere away in Florida."},{"time":51864,"text":"You tell anybody and everybody\nwho will listen,"},{"time":54770,"text":"\"I didn't do it!"},{"time":56257,"text":"I couldn't have done it!"},{"time":58682,"text":"I was hanging out with Mickey\nand Minnie and my kids!\""},{"time":62684,"text":"But no one believes you."},{"time":65284,"text":"Ultimately, you're arrested,"},{"time":67804,"text":"you're tried,"},{"time":69071,"text":"you're convicted"},{"time":70395,"text":"and you are sentenced."},{"time":72278,"text":"And you spend 25 years in jail,"},{"time":76234,"text":"until someone comes along and proves --"},{"time":81564,"text":"has the evidence to prove --"},{"time":83012,"text":"that you actually were in Florida"},{"time":86680,"text":"when this crime was committed."},{"time":89806,"text":"So."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91831,"text":"So, I'm a Harvard Law professor,"},{"time":93509,"text":"and the last several years,\nI have worked on"},{"time":98285,"text":"winning the release of innocent people"},{"time":101373,"text":"who've been wrongfully convicted --"},{"time":104221,"text":"people like Jonathan Fleming,"},{"time":106762,"text":"who spent 24 years, eight months in jail"},{"time":110075,"text":"for a murder that was committed\nin Brooklyn, New York,"},{"time":113697,"text":"while he was in Disney World"},{"time":117204,"text":"with his kids."},{"time":119146,"text":"How do we know this?"},{"time":120882,"text":"Because when he was arrested,"},{"time":123288,"text":"among his property in his back pocket"},{"time":126866,"text":"was a receipt --"},{"time":129045,"text":"time-stamped receipt"},{"time":130886,"text":"that showed that he was in Disney World."},{"time":134322,"text":"That receipt was put in the police file,"},{"time":137471,"text":"a copy of it was put\nin the prosecutor's file,"},{"time":140121,"text":"and they never gave it\nto his public defender."},{"time":143377,"text":"In fact, nobody even knew it was there."},{"time":145343,"text":"It just sat there for 20-some-odd years."},{"time":148926,"text":"My team looked through the file,\nand we found it,"},{"time":153407,"text":"did the rest of the investigation,"},{"time":155153,"text":"and figured out someone else\ncommitted the crime."},{"time":157464,"text":"Mr. Fleming was in Disney World,"},{"time":160628,"text":"and he is now released."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163151,"text":"Let me give you a little bit of context."},{"time":165802,"text":"So about three years ago, I got a call\nfrom the Brooklyn District Attorney."},{"time":169964,"text":"He asked whether I'd be interested\nin designing a program"},{"time":174071,"text":"called a \"conviction review unit.\""},{"time":176073,"text":"So I said yes."},{"time":177378,"text":"A conviction review unit is essentially\na unit in a prosecutor's office"},{"time":182069,"text":"where prosecutors look at their past cases"},{"time":185210,"text":"to determine whether or not\nthey made mistakes."},{"time":188465,"text":"Over the course of the first year,"},{"time":190521,"text":"we found about 13 wrongful convictions,"},{"time":193639,"text":"people having been in jail for decades,"},{"time":196198,"text":"and we released all of them."},{"time":197857,"text":"It was the most in New York history."},{"time":200559,"text":"The program is still going on,"},{"time":202075,"text":"and they're up to 21 releases now --"},{"time":205366,"text":"21 people who spent\nsignificant time behind bars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210257,"text":"So let me tell you about a couple other\nof the men and women"},{"time":215735,"text":"that I interacted with\nin the course of this program."},{"time":219043,"text":"One name is Roger Logan."},{"time":222199,"text":"Mr. Logan had been in jail 17 years"},{"time":225326,"text":"and wrote me a letter."},{"time":226830,"text":"It was a simple letter; it basically said,"},{"time":228997,"text":"\"Professor Sullivan, I'm innocent.\nI've been framed."},{"time":232075,"text":"Can you look at my case?\""},{"time":234279,"text":"At first blush, the case seemed\nlike it was open and shut,"},{"time":237447,"text":"but my research had shown"},{"time":240492,"text":"that single-witness identification cases"},{"time":243139,"text":"are prone to error."},{"time":245377,"text":"It doesn't mean he was innocent,"},{"time":247200,"text":"it just means we ought to look\na little bit closer at those cases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250541,"text":"So we did."},{"time":251875,"text":"And the facts were relatively simple."},{"time":253900,"text":"The eyewitness said she heard a shot,"},{"time":257006,"text":"and she ran to the next building\nand turned around and looked,"},{"time":260081,"text":"and there was Mr. Logan."},{"time":262432,"text":"And he was tried and convicted\nand in jail for 17-some-odd years."},{"time":266740,"text":"But it was a single-witness case,\nso we took a look at it."},{"time":269578,"text":"I sent some people to the scene,\nand there was an inconsistency."},{"time":272722,"text":"And to put it politely:"},{"time":277883,"text":"Usain Bolt couldn't have run\nfrom where she said she was"},{"time":281566,"text":"to the other spot."},{"time":282778,"text":"Right?"},{"time":283954,"text":"So we knew that wasn't true."},{"time":286925,"text":"So it still didn't mean\nthat he didn't do it,"},{"time":289046,"text":"but we knew something was maybe fishy\nabout this witness."},{"time":293634,"text":"So we looked through the file,"},{"time":295692,"text":"a piece of paper in the file\nhad a number on it."},{"time":298055,"text":"The number indicated\nthat this witness had a record."},{"time":301045,"text":"We went back through 20 years\nof non-digitized papers"},{"time":304877,"text":"to figure out what this record was about,"},{"time":307477,"text":"and it turned out -- it turned out --"},{"time":309988,"text":"the eyewitness was in jail"},{"time":313520,"text":"when she said she saw what she saw."},{"time":317718,"text":"The man spent 17 years behind bars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321476,"text":"The last one is a case about two boys,"},{"time":326267,"text":"Willie Stuckey, David McCallum."},{"time":329002,"text":"They were arrested at 15,"},{"time":331320,"text":"and their conviction was vacated\n29 years later."},{"time":336865,"text":"Now this was a case,"},{"time":338683,"text":"once again -- first blush,\nit looked open and shut."},{"time":341511,"text":"They had confessed."},{"time":343750,"text":"But my research showed\nthat juvenile confessions"},{"time":346525,"text":"without a parent present"},{"time":348038,"text":"are prone to error."},{"time":349497,"text":"The DNA cases proved this several times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351787,"text":"So we took a close look."},{"time":353708,"text":"We looked at the confession,"},{"time":355581,"text":"and it turned out,"},{"time":356769,"text":"there was something in the confession"},{"time":358655,"text":"that those boys could not have known."},{"time":360647,"text":"The only people who knew it\nwere police and prosecutors."},{"time":363402,"text":"We knew what really happened;"},{"time":365697,"text":"someone told them to say this."},{"time":367280,"text":"We don't exactly know who,"},{"time":369173,"text":"which person did,"},{"time":370664,"text":"but any rate, the confession was coerced,"},{"time":373583,"text":"we determined."},{"time":375422,"text":"We then went back and did forensics"},{"time":377278,"text":"and did a fulsome investigation"},{"time":378988,"text":"and found that two other,"},{"time":380408,"text":"much older, different heights,\ndifferent hairstyle,"},{"time":383291,"text":"two other people committed the crime,"},{"time":385649,"text":"not these two boys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387341,"text":"I actually went to court that day,"},{"time":389410,"text":"for what's called a \"vacatur hearing,\""},{"time":392976,"text":"where the conviction is thrown out."},{"time":395111,"text":"I went to court; I wanted to see"},{"time":397461,"text":"Mr. McCallum walk out of there."},{"time":399992,"text":"So I went to court,"},{"time":401170,"text":"and the judge said something\nthat judges say all the time,"},{"time":403963,"text":"but this took on a really special meaning."},{"time":406693,"text":"He looked up after the arguments and said,"},{"time":409337,"text":"\"Mr. McCallum,\""},{"time":411108,"text":"he said five beautiful words:"},{"time":413594,"text":"\"You are free to go.\""},{"time":418539,"text":"Can you imagine?"},{"time":420177,"text":"After just about 30 years:"},{"time":423315,"text":"\"You are free to go.\""},{"time":426725,"text":"And he walked out of that courtroom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429595,"text":"Unfortunately,\nhis codefendant, Mr. Stuckey,"},{"time":432799,"text":"didn't get the benefit of that."},{"time":435477,"text":"You see, Mr. Stuckey died in prison"},{"time":438180,"text":"at 34 years old,"},{"time":440292,"text":"and his mother sat\nat counsel table in his place."},{"time":444898,"text":"I'll never forget this\nthe rest of my life."},{"time":447480,"text":"She just rocked at the table, saying,"},{"time":450481,"text":"\"I knew my baby didn't do this."},{"time":452465,"text":"I knew my baby didn't do this.\""},{"time":454708,"text":"And her baby didn't do this."},{"time":456813,"text":"Two other guys did it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459117,"text":"If there's anything that we've learned,\nanything that I've learned,"},{"time":462427,"text":"with this conviction integrity work,"},{"time":465639,"text":"it's that justice doesn't happen."},{"time":469779,"text":"People make justice happen."},{"time":476441,"text":"Justice is not a thing\nthat just descends from above"},{"time":480360,"text":"and makes everything right."},{"time":482602,"text":"If it did, Mr. Stuckey\nwouldn't have died in prison."},{"time":487756,"text":"Justice is something"},{"time":489503,"text":"that people of goodwill make happen."},{"time":493885,"text":"Justice is a decision."},{"time":500392,"text":"Justice is a decision."},{"time":503461,"text":"We make justice happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506306,"text":"You know, the scary thing is,"},{"time":508249,"text":"in each of these three cases I described,"},{"time":510890,"text":"it would have only taken\njust an extra minute --"},{"time":513516,"text":"an extra minute --"},{"time":515155,"text":"for someone to look through the file"},{"time":517322,"text":"and find this receipt."},{"time":519804,"text":"Just one -- to look through the file,\nfind the receipt,"},{"time":523684,"text":"give it to the public defender."},{"time":526882,"text":"It would have taken someone just a minute"},{"time":529448,"text":"to look at the video confession\nand say, \"That cannot be.\""},{"time":535179,"text":"Just a minute."},{"time":537704,"text":"And perhaps Mr. Stuckey\nwould be alive today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541451,"text":"It reminds me of one of my favorite poems."},{"time":544856,"text":"It's a poem that Benjamin Elijah Mays\nwould always recite,"},{"time":549163,"text":"and he called it \"God's Minute.\""},{"time":550900,"text":"And it goes something like this:"},{"time":552497,"text":"\"I have only just a minute,"},{"time":554638,"text":"only 60 seconds in it,"},{"time":556689,"text":"forced upon me, can't refuse it,"},{"time":558988,"text":"didn't seek it, didn't choose it."},{"time":561278,"text":"But it's up to me to use it."},{"time":562856,"text":"I must suffer if I lose it,\ngive account if I abuse it."},{"time":567175,"text":"Just a tiny little minute,"},{"time":570105,"text":"but eternity is in it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":573903,"text":"If I were to charge"},{"time":575477,"text":"each and every one of us,"},{"time":577934,"text":"I would want to say something like,"},{"time":581962,"text":"\"Every day,"},{"time":583868,"text":"every day,"},{"time":585935,"text":"take just one extra minute"},{"time":589800,"text":"and do some justice."},{"time":592932,"text":"You don't have to --"},{"time":594358,"text":"I mean, some people spend\ntheir careers and their lives,"},{"time":598395,"text":"like public defenders,"},{"time":599657,"text":"doing justice every day."},{"time":602206,"text":"But in your professional lives,\nwhatever you do,"},{"time":604550,"text":"take time out"},{"time":606264,"text":"to just"},{"time":608576,"text":"do some justice."},{"time":609887,"text":"Make a colleague feel better."},{"time":612083,"text":"If you hear something that's sexist,"},{"time":615388,"text":"don't laugh, speak up."},{"time":618397,"text":"If someone is down, lift them up,"},{"time":620741,"text":"one extra minute each day,"},{"time":624253,"text":"and it'll be a great, great place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":626599,"text":"I want to show you something."},{"time":629957,"text":"Now, above me is a picture"},{"time":632956,"text":"of David McCallum."},{"time":635353,"text":"This is the day\nhe was released from prison."},{"time":638257,"text":"After 30 years, he got to hug a niece"},{"time":641338,"text":"he had never been able to touch before."},{"time":645378,"text":"And I asked him then,"},{"time":647563,"text":"I said, \"What's the first thing\nyou want to do?\""},{"time":650286,"text":"And he said, \"I just want\nto walk on the sidewalk"},{"time":652689,"text":"without anybody telling me where to go.\""},{"time":655470,"text":"Wasn't bitter,"},{"time":657199,"text":"just wanted to walk on the sidewalk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659835,"text":"I spoke to Mr. McCallum\nabout two weeks ago."},{"time":663369,"text":"I went to New York."},{"time":664567,"text":"It was on the two-year anniversary"},{"time":667354,"text":"of his release."},{"time":669280,"text":"And we talked,"},{"time":670944,"text":"we laughed, we hugged, we cried."},{"time":674035,"text":"And he's doing quite well."},{"time":676264,"text":"And one of the things he said\nwhen we met with him"},{"time":680174,"text":"is that he now has dedicated his life"},{"time":683328,"text":"and his career"},{"time":684721,"text":"to ensuring that nobody else\nis locked up unjustly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":689951,"text":"Justice, my friends,"},{"time":693596,"text":"is a decision."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695526,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":696757,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}